hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Which university are you at? diamox online canada why not back this up with hard facts. Evidenced based practice is required from almost all policies and procedures in hospitals, especially to do with nursing. I want to see the numbers on just how many hospitalized patients actually contract "influenza" from healthcare workers. This is almost a form of bullying and it's a total scare tactic that I don't believe has the evidence to back it up. I feel violated and sad. Big Brother for sure. I hope this ends up in court. I'd like to see it thrown out.
